oyoyo irc lib 
-------------

The oyoyo irc library is a small, simple irc lib for python suitable for bots, clients and anything else you can think of (even games).

    * clean and simple design
    * multi-server, multi-room
    * autoreconnect
    * timed callbacks
    * and not a thread in sight! 


Install
-------

the usual

    $ python setup.py install

or for developers

    $ python setup.py develop --install-dir=/some/path
    

